#: ../../data/txts/README.lua:19
msgid ""
"Widelands is nearly feature complete and is much fun to play alone and even "
"more in multiplayer with others. Still, there is always more work to be done"
" in all areas. If you are interested in contributing – be it by making "
"graphics, fixing bugs or adding new features, translating the game into your"
" language or creating new maps – get in touch on our homepage."
msgstr "Tha sinn air cha mhòr a h-uile gleus a tha fainear dhuinn airson Widelands a chruthachadh is tha e tlachdmhor ri chluiche ’nad aonar no le daoine eile sa mhodh ioma-chluicheadair. Tha barrachd obrach ri dèanamh an-còmhnaidh co-dhiù sna h-uile roinn. Nam bu toigh leat taic a thoirt dhuinn – ge b’ e an dèan thu grafaigeachd, an càraich thu bugaichean, an cuir thu gleusan ùra ris, an eadar-theangaich thu dhan chànan agad fhèin e no an cruthaich thu mapaichean ùra – dèan conaltradh rinn air an làrach-lìn againn."

