#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:11
msgid "You are in the multiplayer launch game menu."
msgstr "Tha thu sa chlàr-taice gus geama ioma-chluicheadair a thòiseachadh."

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:13
msgid "Client settings"
msgstr "Roghainnean a’ chliant"

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:14
msgid ""
"On the left side is a list of all clients including you. You can set your "
"role with the button following your nickname. Available roles are:"
msgstr "Tha liosta dhe na h-uile cliant air an tabh deas, a’ gabhail a-steach thu fhèin. ’S urrainn dhut do dhreuchd a shuidheachadh leis a’ phutan às dèidh d’ far-ainm. Seo na dreuchdan a tha ri làimh:"

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:15
msgid ""
"The player with the color of the flag. If more than one client selected the "
"same color, these share control over the player (‘shared kingdom mode’)."
msgstr "An cluicheadair aig a bheil bratach leis an dath seo. Ma thagh barrachd air aon chliant an aon dath, bidh smachd aca còmhla air a’ chluicheadair (“modh rìoghachd co-phàirteach”)."

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:16
msgid ""
"Spectator mode, meaning you can see everything, but cannot control any "
"player."
msgstr "Modh amhairc, ’s e seo gum faic thu a h-uile rud ach cha bhi smachd agad air cluicheadair."

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:18
msgid "Player settings"
msgstr "Roghainnean a’ chluicheadair"

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:19
msgid ""
"In the middle are the settings for the players. To start a game, each player"
" must be one of the following:"
msgstr "Tha roghainnean nan cluicheadairean sa mheadhan. Feumaidh gach cluicheadair a bhith aon dhe na rudan seo mus gabh geama a thòiseachadh:"

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:20
msgid "Connected to one or more clients (see ‘Client settings’)."
msgstr "Ceangailte ri cliant no dhà (seall air “Roghainnean a’ chliant”)."

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:21
msgid ""
"Connected to a computer player (the face in the picture as well as the mouse"
" hover texts indicate the strength of the currently selected computer "
"player)."
msgstr "Ceangailte ri cluicheadair coimpiutair (innsidh an dà chuid an t-aodann san dealbh is an teacsa nuair a chumas tu an luchag os a chionn dè cho làidir ’s a tha an cluicheadair coimpiutair a thagh thu an-dràsta)."

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:22
msgid "Set as shared in starting position for another player."
msgstr "’Na cho-phàirteach ann an ionad-tòiseachaidh airson cluicheadair eile."

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:23
msgid "Closed."
msgstr "Dùinte."

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:24
msgid ""
"The latter three can only be set by the hosting client by left-clicking the "
"‘type’ button of a player. Hosting players can also set the initialization "
"of each player (the set of buildings, wares and workers the player starts "
"with) and the tribe and team for computer players."
msgstr "Cha ghabh an trì rud mu dheireadh dhiubh a shuidheachadh ach leis a’ chliant a bhios ’na òstair ’s esan a’ briogadh leis a’ phutan clì air putan “seòrsa” aig cluicheadair. ’S urrainn do chluicheadairean òstair an tòiseachadh aig gach cluicheadair (an seata de thogalaichean, bhathar is obraichean leis an tòisich an cluicheadair) agus treubh is sgioba nan cluicheadairean coimpiutair a rèiteachadh cuideachd."

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:25
msgid ""
"Every client connected to a player (who isn’t a spectator) can set the tribe"
" and the team for that player."
msgstr "’S urrainn do gach cliant a bhios ceangailte ri cluicheadair (nach eil ’na amharc) treubh is sgioba a’ chluicheadair sin a shuidheachadh."

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:27
msgid "Map details"
msgstr "Fiosrachadh a’ mhapa"

#: ../../data/txts/help/multiplayer_help.lua:28
msgid ""
"You can see information about the selected map or savegame on the right-hand"
" side. A button next to the map name allows the host to change to a "
"different map. Furthermore, the host is able to set a specific win "
"condition, and finally can start the game as soon as all players are set up."
msgstr "Chì thu fiosrachadh mun mhapa no geama air a shàbhaladh taobh deas. Leigidh putan ri taobh ainm a’ mhapa leis an òstair atharrachadh gu fear eile. ’S urrainn dhan òstair cuideachd cumha na buaidhe a shuidheachadh is an geama a thòiseachadh nuair a bhios gach cluicheadair ullamh."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/atlanteans.lua:4
msgid ""
"Keep an eye on your fishers and build a fish breeder’s house. After fish "
"resources are exhausted in their work area, the fish supply cannot be "
"regenerated."
msgstr "Cum sùil air na h-iasgairean agad agus tog ionad-àraich èisg. Nuair nach eil iasg san raointean-obrach aca tuilleadh, cha ghabh stòras nan iasg ath-ghintinn."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/atlanteans.lua:8
msgid ""
"Always build a forester’s and a woodcutter’s house, so you will not run out "
"of logs."
msgstr "Tog taigh planntair-choille is taigh buaineadair-fhiodha an-còmhnaidh ach nach ruith am fiodh ort."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/barbarians.lua:4 ../../data/txts/tips/empire.lua:4
msgid ""
"Keep an eye on your fishers. After fish resources are exhausted in their "
"work area, they will stop fishing."
msgstr "Cum sùil air na h-iasgairean agad. Sguiridh iad dhen iasgach nuair nach eil iasg san raon-obrach aca tuilleadh."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/barbarians.lua:8
msgid ""
"Always build a ranger’s and a gamekeeper’s hut, so you will not run out of "
"logs or game."
msgstr "Tog bothan maoir-choille is bothan-geamair an-còmhnaidh ach nach ruith am fiodh no sitheann ort."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/editor.lua:4
msgid ""
"You can find general help for the editor as well as a short tutorial on our "
"wiki at www.widelands.org"
msgstr "Gheibh thu cobhair choitcheann airson an deasaiche cho math ri oideachadh goirid san uicidh againn air www.widelands.org"

#: ../../data/txts/tips/editor.lua:8
msgid ""
"You can select multiple animal types if you hold down Ctrl during selection."
" If you then click on the map, an instance of one of the selected animal "
"types will be placed."
msgstr "’S urrainn dhut iomadh seòrsa de bheathach a thaghadh aig an aon àm ’s tu a’ cumail Ctrl sìos fhad ’s a bhios tu ’gan taghadh. Ma nì thu briogadh air a’ mhapa an uairsin, thèid ball dhe aon dhe na seòrsaichean de bheathach a thagh thu a chur ann."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/editor.lua:12
msgid ""
"Just like with animals, you can also select multiple immovables or ground "
"textures with Ctrl + mouse click."
msgstr "Mar as urrainn dhut le beathaichean, ’s urrainn dhut iomadh nì do-ghluasad no cruth-tìre a thaghadh le Ctrl + briogadh."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/editor.lua:16
msgid ""
"Holding down Shift switches the first alternative tool on. This tool is in "
"most cases the complete opposite of the normal tool (for example deletion of"
" an object instead of placing one)."
msgstr "Bidh an dàrna inneal dàrnach an comas fhad ’s a chumas tu Shift sìos. Mar as trice, ’s e an dearbh chaochladh aig an inneal àbhaisteach a th’ ann (mar eisimpleir, sguabaidh tu oibseact às seach a bhith ’ga chur ris)."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/editor.lua:20
msgid ""
"Holding down Alt switches the second alternative tool on (if it exists)."
msgstr "Ma chumas tu Alt sìos, nì seo suids dhan inneal dàrnach eile (ma tha seo ann)."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/editor.lua:24
msgid ""
"The number keys (0 - 9) allow you to directly set the size of the selected "
"area around your mouse cursor."
msgstr "’S urrainn dhut meud an raoin a thèid a thaghadh mu chùrsair na luchaige agad a shuidheachadh sa bhad leis na h-iuchraichean àireimh (0 - 9)."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/editor.lua:28
msgid ""
"Space key behaves like in normal game. It switches if building spaces are "
"shown on or off."
msgstr "Nì an iuchair Space na nì e ann an geama àbhaisteach. Nochdaidh no falaichidh e na h-ionadan togail."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/empire.lua:8
msgid "Always build a forester’s house so you will not run out of logs."
msgstr "Tog taigh planntair-coille an-còmhnaidh ach nach ruith am fiodh ort."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:4
msgid ""
"The building process will only start after a road is built to the "
"construction site."
msgstr "Cha tòisich an togail mus dèid rathad a thogail dhan làrach togail."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:8
msgid ""
"Be sure to send a geologist to survey sites before building a well or a "
"mine."
msgstr "Dèan cinnteach gun cuir thu clach-eòlaiche airson làraichean a rùrachadh mus tog thu tobar no mèinn."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:12
msgid ""
"Your territory can be expanded by building various military buildings – "
"Sentry, Fortress, Blockhouse, etc."
msgstr "’S urrainn dhut barrachd ranntair a ghabhail ma thogas tu togalaichean an airm a leithid freiceadanan, dùin, taighean-bloca agus msaa."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:16
msgid "Miners will work only if supplied with food."
msgstr "Cha dèan na mèinnearan obair ach ma gheibh iad biadh."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:20
msgid ""
"Split your roads into shorter sections by planting some flags. This will "
"speed up transportation of your wares."
msgstr "Tog brataich gus na rathaidean agad a roinneadh ann an roinnean goirid. Thèid am bathar a ghiùlan nas luaithe an uairsin."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:24
msgid ""
"Any further questions? Our FAQ, the wiki and of course our community forums "
"can be found at www.widelands.org."
msgstr "A bheil ceist sam bith eile agad? Thoir sùil air na CÀBHA, an uicidh is am bòrd-brath air www.widelands.org."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:28
msgid ""
"Use the priority buttons in building windows to adjust delivery of a "
"specific ware."
msgstr "Cleachd putanan a’ phrìomhachais ann an uinneag togalaich gus gleus a chur air lìbhrigeadh bathair shònraichte."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:32
msgid ""
"Use the ‘configure economy’ menu to adjust the target quantity of wares. It "
"can be accessed via the flag menu."
msgstr "Cleachd an clàr-taice “Rèitich an eaconamaidh” gus gleus a chur air co mheud dhen bhathar a tha thu ag amas. Gheibh thu inntrigeadh dha le clàran-taice nam bratach."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:36
msgid ""
"Manage your messages more efficiently: press ‘N’ for News to access the "
"messages window, then use ‘G’ for Go To, and the Delete key to archive "
"messages."
msgstr "Stiùirich na teachdaireachdan agad nas èifeachdaiche: brùth air “N” airson naidheachdan gus uinneag nan teachdaireachdan inntrigeadh is an uairsin cleachd “G” airson dol gu teachdaireachd is an iuchair Delete gus teachdaireachdan a chur dhan tasglann."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:40
msgid ""
"Press Ctrl+(0-9) to store important locations, then press 0-9 to recall "
"them."
msgstr "Brùth Ctrl+(0-9) gus ionadan cudromach a stòradh is brùth air 0-9 an uairsin gus dol ann."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:44
msgid ""
"Removing a road while holding Ctrl lets you remove all flags up to the first"
" junction."
msgstr "’S urrainn dhut gach bratach gun chiad ghobhal a thoirt air falbh ’s tu a’ cumail sìos CTRL fhad ’s a bhios tu a’ toirt rathad air falbh."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:48
msgid ""
"New soldiers are recruited in a barracks. Their abilities can then be "
"improved in training sites."
msgstr "Trusaidh tu saighdearan ùra ann an taigh-feachd. ’S urrainn dhut piseach a thoirt air na comasan aca sna h-ionadan-oideachaidh an uairsin."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:52
msgid ""
"If you like to live dangerously, pressing Ctrl while clicking the enhance, "
"dismantle or destroy building buttons will skip the confirmation."
msgstr "Ma tha thu coma mu chunnart, ma chumas tu Ctrl sìos ’s tu a’ briogadh air putan leasachaidh, millidh no toirt às a chèile an togalaich, gearraidh tu leum thairis air an dearbhadh."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:56
msgid "Press I to quickly toggle the display of your stock inventory."
msgstr "Brùth air I gus uinneag an stòrais a thoglachadh gu luath."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:60
msgid ""
"An economy consists of all buildings and flags connected by roads. The "
"supplies and demands of buildings are handled in its economy."
msgstr "Togaidh tu eaconamaidh le togalaichean is brataich a bhios ceangailte le rathaidean. Thèid an saothrachadh is na feumalachdan aig togalach a làimhseachadh taobh a-staigh an eaconamaidh aige."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/general_game.lua:64
msgid ""
"Some buildings, such as the farm, have a very small work area. If the "
"building is surrounded with trees or roads, production will stop."
msgstr "Tha raon-obrach glè bheag aig cuid a thogalaichean, can an tuathanas. Ma thèid an togalach a chuairteachadh le craobhan no rathaidean, cha shaothraich e bathar tuilleadh."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/multiplayer.lua:4
msgid ""
"You can use the ’Page up’ and ‘Page down’ keys to adjust your desired speed "
"– the real speed is then democratically set."
msgstr "’S urrainn dhut na h-iuchraichean “Page up” is “Page down” a chleachdadh gus gleus a chur air luaths a gheama – thèid an luaths da-rìribh a shuidheachadh gu deamocratach an uairsin."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/multiplayer.lua:8
msgid ""
"You can use ‘/me’ at the beginning of a chatmessage: ‘/me is tired’ will be "
"printed as ‘-> Nickname is tired’."
msgstr "’S urrainn dhut /me a chleachdadh aig toiseach teachdaireachd na cabadaich. Thèid “/me a tha sgìth” a shealltainn mar “-> far-ainm a tha sgìth”."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/multiplayer.lua:12
msgid ""
"Use ‘@name’ at the beginning of a chat message to send it to only one "
"player."
msgstr "Cleachd “@name” aig toiseach teachdaireachd na cabadaich gus a cur gu aonar chluicheadair a-mhàin."

#: ../../data/txts/tips/singleplayer.lua:4
msgid ""
"Our computer players are too boring? Visit our website at www.widelands.org "
"and meet other players to play online."
msgstr "An cuir na cluicheadairean coimpiutair againn ’nad chadal thu? Tadhail air an làrach-lìn againn air www.widelands.org is tachair ri cluicheadairean eile gus cluiche air loidhne."
